### Stage 28：手动 URL 使用 Firecrawl 提取（不回写文章）
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/extractions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: idea-stage28-firecrawl-001

{"articleId":null,"url":"https://spring.io/blog","method":"FIRECRAWL"}

### Stage 28：把文章 550 用 Playwright 重新提取并回写
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/extractions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: idea-stage28-playwright-001

{"articleId":550,"url":"https://example.org/public-article","method":"PLAYWRIGHT"}

### 查询文章 550 的提取历史
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/extractions?articleId=550&limit=30
Accept: application/json

### 重试提取任务 1
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/extractions/1/retry
Accept: application/json

### 查看提取任务 1 的原始 HTML
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/extractions/1/raw
Accept: text/plain

### Stage 29：上传文章 550 的补充材料
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/evidence-files
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=Stage29Boundary
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: idea-stage29-upload-001

--Stage29Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="ownerType"

ARTICLE
--Stage29Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="ownerId"

550
--Stage29Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="fileKind"

SUPPLEMENT
--Stage29Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="verification-note.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8

2026-07-18：已与公开原始页面交叉验证。
--Stage29Boundary--

### 查询文章 550 的全部证据版本
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/evidence-files?ownerType=ARTICLE&ownerId=550
Accept: application/json

### 下载证据文件 1
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/evidence-files/1/download
Accept: application/octet-stream
